::Spears::

She whimpered softly as she leaked on the floor.  She felt scared and 
hurt. She cried softly on the floor as she saw her own mech fluid 
spread under her, across the floor. She brought her hands up and 
covered her face as she cried.  The shot had hit one of her major 
pain censors and it was overwhelming her.
